[1] Florida
Date: Sat 3 Apr 2021
Source: Equnews [edited]
https://equnews.com/rhinoENG/once-again-horse-tested-positive-for-ehv-1-in-florida


At the competition of the Winter Equestrian Festival in Florida, another horse has tested positive for rhino. A few weeks ago, this was also the case. The horse had a fever on Thursday [1 Apr 2021] but showed no clinical signs. Three corridors in the stable tent have been quarantined. The organization itself came out with the news.

Thursday [1 Apr 2021] the horse was tested because of the fever, and the nose test was positive. The blood test was negative. The horse was taken to the Florida clinic.

